  "description" : "* Based on a fantasy slice of life manga by http://anidb.net/cr85201 [Yukishiro Ichi].\nIn a faraway land, there exists a forest where all manner of beings go to dispose of their trash. One day, a young girl named Eve is abandoned along with the usual debris, but she is quickly found by an aging dragon who decides to take her in and raise her as its own. Under this ancient being`s watchful eye, Eve grows up happy and healthy, but soon their peaceful life together is interrupted by impending tragedy. Yet months later, Eve does something truly astonishing for the sake of reuniting with her dragon guardian...\nSource: Seven Seas Entertainment",
